Document: EditorInspector
Path: godot/classes/class_editorinspector.rst
Summary: Properties of the EditorInspector class, including focus and scroll behavior.

Properties:
* draw_focus_border (bool): Controls whether a focus border is drawn. Default: true. (overrides ScrollContainer.draw_focus_border)
* focus_mode (FocusMode): Determines how the control gains focus. Default: 2. (overrides Control.focus_mode)
* follow_focus (bool): Determines if the inspector should follow the focus. Default: true. (overrides ScrollContainer.follow_focus)
* horizontal_scroll_mode (ScrollMode): Controls the behavior of horizontal scrolling. Default: 0. (overrides ScrollContainer.horizontal_scroll_mode)
